"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The hostilities come during a fragile ceasefire between the US and Iran, with ongoing negotiations to end the three-month war. The military has declared areas south of the Zahrani River as combat zones and is threatening Hezbollah with new strikes.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fragile Ceasefire\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las peleas pasan durante una tregua fr\u00e1gil entre Estados Unidos e Ir\u00e1n, con negociaciones para terminar la guerra de tres meses. El ej\u00e9rcito ha dicho que las \u00e1reas al sur del r\u00edo Zahrani son zonas de combate y est\u00e1 amenazando a Hezbollah con nuevos ataques.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tregua Fr\u00e1gil\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Hamas reports that Mohammed Odeh was killed along with his wife and two children in a strike on a residential building.\",            \"english_title\": \"Family Killed in Strike\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hamas dice que Mohammed Odeh muri\u00f3 junto con su esposa y dos hijos en un ataque a un edificio residencial.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Familia Muerta en Ataque\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus mentioned that fighting in DR Congo is making it difficult to stop the spread of diseases.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fighting in DR Congo\",            \"translated_version\": \"Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus dijo que las peleas en el Congo hacen dif\u00edcil detener la propagaci\u00f3n de enfermedades.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Peleas en el Congo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Nine people were injured and another nine are missing after a tank ruptured at a paper mill in Longview, Washington.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tank Rupture Incident\",            \"translated_version\": \"Nueve personas resultaron heridas y otras nueve est\u00e1n desaparecidas despu\u00e9s de que un tanque se rompi\u00f3 en una f\u00e1brica de papel en Longview, Washington.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incidente de Tanque Roto\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Italian Supreme Court dismissed a tourist's claim that her consumer rights were violated when she was only offered \u20ac7 bottled mineral water.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tourist's Claim Dismissed\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Corte Suprema de Italia rechaz\u00f3 la queja de una turista que dijo que sus derechos de consumidor fueron violados cuando solo le ofrecieron agua mineral embotellada de 7 euros.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Queja de Turista Rechazada\"        }    ]}"